# ==============================================================================
# PRODUCT INTELLIGENCE OS ENVIRONMENT SETTINGS
# ==============================================================================

# 1. AI Reasoning & Embedding Layer (Required for Live LLM Operations)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Paste your OpenAI API Key here. 
# If left blank, the application automatically triggers the high-fidelity
# "Intelligence Simulator" fallback, allowing 100% testability out-of-the-box!
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# 2. Production Database Deployment: Cloudflare D1 (SQLite)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# In development, the app runs on a zero-setup local file-based database:
# File Path: src/lib/data-store.json (Auto-initialized and Auto-seeded!)
#
# When deploying to production on Cloudflare Pages, bind your D1 Database:
# In your wrangler.toml or Cloudflare Dashboard, bind:
# DB = "YOUR_D1_DATABASE_ID"
#
# To execute D1 schema migrations:
# npx wrangler d1 execute product-intel-db --local --file=src/lib/data-store.json

# 3. Production Vector Space: Cloudflare Vectorize
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# In development, the app runs a custom 1536-dimensional cosine-similarity 
# search engine in TypeScript.
#
# When deploying to production on Cloudflare Workers/Pages, create a Vectorize index:
# npx wrangler vectorize create product-vector-index --dimensions=1536 --metric=cosine
